name: Furnished Stays
overview: When you are looking to stay in Sydney for a long or short term visit, Furnished Stays has a range of corporate housing options to suit you. Our strong knowledge of the area, as well as our experience finding tailored solutions to every individual we help, allows us to find executive accommodation that suits your specific needs. So whether you are looking for a corporate apartment in the city centre for your 3 month stay or you are travelling to a conference over the weekend and want to be in close vicinity of the event, Furnished Stays can help.
